properties.description:
STAY INFORMED: Beerwah bushfire as at 11.30am Mon 17 May        Bushfire warning level: ADVICE     Queensland Fire and Emergency Services (QFES) advises there is a bushfire in Beerwah. You need to keep up to date and decide what actions you will take if the situation changes.    Currently as at 11.30am Monday 17 May, a bushfire is travelling along Old Gympie Road near Lindeman Road.     People in the area will be affected by smoke, which will reduce visibility and air quality.     Properties are not under direct threat at this time. Call Triple Zero (000) immediately if you believe you or your property is under threat.
